    <!-- HELP DIALOG -->
    <string name="card_match_instruction">Find matching pairs of fruits while avoiding bombs! You have 90 seconds to earn as many stars as you can.\n\nHow to play:\n• At the start of each level, the cards are shown for 2 seconds – try to remember as many as possible before they flip over.\n• Tap cards to reveal them – select two to see if they match.\n• Matching pairs stay uncovered; mismatched ones flip back after a moment.\n• Watch out for bombs! Hitting one will cost you 10 seconds.\n\nBonuses:\n• Earn a star for every correctly matched pair.\n• Gain an extra 30 seconds for completing a level.</string>
    <string name="color_sequence_instruction">Repeat the shown sequence of colored buttons! You have 90 seconds to earn as many stars as you can.\n\nHow to play:\n• At the start of each round, a sequence of buttons is shown – each one has a unique color and sound.\n• After the preview, repeat the sequence by tapping the buttons in the same order.\n• If you make a mistake, the sequence will replay automatically.\n• The timer pauses during the preview and runs only during your turn.\n\nBonuses:\n• Earn a star for every correctly repeated sequence.\n• Gain an extra 15 seconds for completing a level.</string>

    <string name="number_addition_instruction">Select numbers whose sum equals the displayed result! You have 90 seconds to earn as many stars as you can.\n\nHow to play:\n• Tap number buttons to select them – purple means selected.\n• Choose the required number of buttons to check your answer – a correct combination turns gray permanently, while an incorrect one flashes red and resets after a moment.\n• Some levels include extra cards that are not needed to reach the target sum.\n\nBonuses:\n• Earn a star for every correctly found sum.\n• Gain an extra 20 seconds for completing a level.</string>
